    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以女子学校为背景的生存试炼游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家将参加多场试炼，<br>每一场都有不同的目标与条件。<br>一旦失败，将立刻被淘汰。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着试炼的进行，参与者不断减少，<br>最终只有一人能够毕业。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >真实的女子学校环境与令人不安的氛围营造</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >短小却高度紧张的游戏体验</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每场试炼都有不同的规则与失败条件</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >需要精准时机、观察力与操作技巧的玩法</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏时长：根据游玩方式约60～90分钟</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多结局：无</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>9名少女</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249570/extras/aa309dbe906755c1965ca861e70f09f4.poster.avif?t=1772378889\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249570/extras/aa309dbe906755c1965ca861e70f09f4.webm?t=1772378889\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249570/extras/aa309dbe906755c1965ca861e70f09f4.mp4?t=1772378889\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>8场试炼</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249570/extras/b326f799d1bf17da4b6ea1e04535eff1.poster.avif?t=1772378889\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249570/extras/b326f799d1bf17da4b6ea1e04535eff1.webm?t=1772378889\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249570/extras/b326f799d1bf17da4b6ea1e04535eff1.mp4?t=1772378889\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>以及，死亡</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249570/extras/713bd5197a64f7487a729351c3b03bf3.poster.avif?t=1772378889\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249570/extras/713bd5197a64f7487a729351c3b03bf3.webm?t=1772378889\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249570/extras/713bd5197a64f7487a729351c3b03bf3.mp4?t=1772378889\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >反应力、记忆力、判断力、观察力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的全部能力都将被置于考验之中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过所有试炼，<br>成为最后的毕业生。</p>",
